<div class="homepage">
  <div class="row featurette">
    <div class="col-md-7">
      <h2 class="featurette-heading heading-font-dark">Getting Started is easy. <span class="text-muted">Here's how...</span></h2>
      <p class="hp-p">Use the search field to browse the works of thousands of artists from across the United States and Canada.  You can search by artist, name of work, or by descriptive terms like "landscape," "acrylic," or even "cheerful."</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-5">
      <%= image_tag "search.jpg", class: "featurette-image img-responsive img-about-top" %>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <hr class="featurette-divider">
  
  <div class="row featurette">
    <div class="col-md-5">
      <%= image_tag "mosaicexample.png", class: "featurette-image img-responsive img-about-middle" %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-7">
      <h2 class="featurette-heading heading-font-dark">Create your own mosaic. <span class="text-muted">(This is where it gets fun.)</span></h2>
      <p class="hp-p">Signup allows you to create your own user page where you can start a collection, or "mosaic," of all the works you like.  You'll have a convenient place to access your favorite art--and you can bookmark your favorite artists to see their newest works as soon as they're finished.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="featurette-divider">
  
  <div class="row featurette">
    <div class="col-md-7">
      <h2 class="featurette-heading heading-font-dark">Are you an artist? <span class="text-muted">Reach new audiences.</span></h2>
      <p class="lead">Art lovers use WhereArtThou to connect with their favorite artists--add your collections to WhereArtThou, along with pricing and contact information to instantly get your art in front of new people--and new customers.  Sign up, select "artist" and we'll help you set up your own searchable gallery.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-5">
      <%= image_tag "hpimage3_thou.jpg", class: "featurette-image img-responsive img-about-bottom" %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
      <% if !user_signed_in? %>
        <div class="home-page-buttons">
          <div class="container action-header">
            <h2>Get started now.</h2>
          </div>
          <%= render 'layouts/discover_modal' %>
          <%= link_to 'SIGN UP', '#', data: {toggle: 'modal', target: '#myModal'}, class: "btn btn-success btn-lg hpbutton" %>
        </div>
      <% else %>
        <div class="container action-header">
        </div>
      <% end %>
</div>


</div>